## ğŸ› ï¸ Philosophy

CloudChain takes the chaos out of cloud backup by enforcing discipline:
	â€¢	No ad-hoc accounts
	â€¢	No mystery folders
	â€¢	No hidden state

Just a clean, deterministic chain of accounts you can audit at a glance.
